global_attributes.comment: This deployment (R00004) consists of two smaller deployments: a cross-shelf transect from 2017-06-10T12:15 to 2017-06-11T00:36 and an along-shelf transect from 2017-06-11T02:44 to 2017-06-11T23:17UTC. These files are associated with the across-shelf transect. This mission was aborted at approximately 2017-06-10 13:19:00 UTC to correct mission parameters. The mission was resumed at approximately 2017-06-10 14:20:00 UTC. Only data collected after the mission was resumed are ingested.
